(## 1. Project Information) Tj T*
(BudgetBuddy is a multi-platform budgeting app for personal transactions and shared expenses.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(## 2. Refactoring Summary) Tj T*
(- Architecture changed from: Layer-based controller/service packages) Tj T*
(- Architecture changed to: Vertical Slice packages under backend features) Tj T*
(- Google OAuth-compatible callback flow added as an optional login method) Tj T*
(- UI redesigned with Soft Bloom Pastel theme) Tj T*
(- Uniform card component system with sticky headers and scrollable bodies added to the web UI) Tj T*
(- Android screens updated to use the same pastel palette and card-like containers) Tj T*
() Tj T*
